reviewText:
My son enjoys Ultraman. the video has plenty of extras and information on the filming
a lot of action for Ultraman fans

We  know what we want when we order this kind of flick and I feel that this delivered in many ways...I really enjoyed it from several different levels really...
Good stuff...

A Must see Movie!!! If you are a Sci-Fi fan, or an Ultraman fan as well, you Must Buy this movie. It Unites the first Ultra Brothers of the series (Ultraman, Ultraseven, Ultraman Jack, Ultraman Ace, Ultraman taro, and Ultraman Zoffy.)to help their younguest Ultra-brother, and newest protector of earth, Ultraman Mebius. The story is very good, the action is great, and the fighting of the Ultra-brothers is spectacular!. Do Not Miss This Movie, It's A Real Must Have movie!!! I Guarantee it!!!.
